{"type": "article", "id": 27524, "title": "有湿地有沙场，这所澳大利亚的小学鼓励孩子接触大自然", "description": "运用自然光线和温暖的颜色，让空间变得受欢迎。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-30T13:34:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4384, "name": "学校"}, {"id": 5534, "name": "澳大利亚"}, {"id": 28313, "name": "Guildford Grammar School"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 167, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120702xCiVKbOG6eTzr7nu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>越来越多的学校或幼儿园开始思考如何“寓教于乐”，不仅仅是改变教学设施，也开始从建筑上重新设计。其中一个有趣的案例是手塚贵晴和手塚由比夫妇设计的东京 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26576.html\">Fuji Kindergarten（富士幼儿园）</a>，拥有倾斜屋顶的椭圆形建筑本身也是游乐场，在爬树、观察滑落雨水等细节中既激发玩乐天性，也能近距离接触自然。</p>\n<p>而在澳大利亚的珀斯（Perth），吉尔福德文法学校（Guildford Grammar School ）新开放了它的预科班（<a href=\"http://www.ggs.wa.edu.au/About-Us/Our-School/Preparatory-School/Our-New-Preparatory-School-Buildings\">Preparatory School</a>）。这所学校提供从幼儿园到 6 年级的学生学习，修建的核心目的是启发学生。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>负责修建的 <a href=\"http://www.christou.com.au/portfolio/latest-projects/guildford-grammar-preparatory-school\">Christou Design Group </a>并没有建造大型的楼房或者游乐设施，而是用 4 幢两层楼的建筑作为主体，中间留出了大量的绿化面积作为庭院，拥有一种更自然的环境。使得阳光可以大面积照射到建筑本身，也保持了良好的空气流通。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120652l4RtCS7jfJXLTdNV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">湿地环境上的学校</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120653JIwdvCNaZrPXEmsg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>在这个有环形溪水的地方，可以与水嬉戏，白色的沙地里有一系列玩乐设施，这里也将学生聚集起来以促进互动交流。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021206538NL93XhFMTwB7ejU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120654QjVdN9ixlBuRW5qE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120654ClecTh235vsmpGDi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>建筑的外立面是砖和镀锌材料相错的结构，形状较为方正，流露出一种古典优雅的气质。其中三幢教学建筑都带有“翅膀”，在红砖墙的侧面延伸出玻璃窗，也有助于光线进入空间。“翅膀”里面对应的是一个用彩色软垫包裹的沙发，大教室里面的座位也是活动的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120655SkmAhY0LuTGoINUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120656JI6rSx49bCzAVqiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120656XYDAKrIyGNE3P7ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120657hQZn9foJ36LaVvHX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120658TQ6Lo0S3s2xvGmeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120658UTLyWd2IRuD5pbjG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">“翅膀”下的沙发空间</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>室内其他地方也布置成彩色的，间隔以胶合板，使跳跃的色彩有一个温暖的中和。修建者称“运用自然光线和温暖的颜色，可以让空间变得受欢迎。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120659bsX3OvDj6w5tc82z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120659CyH8pSL6dUwZF3a0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120700kdpAUFhIe4zZl5R6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120700CFRbVYEPJvOMUk7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120701covtUP54QaW2EOeK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120701Y5OsWQFeumwnjbJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120702dIUY3p02zsMaRZOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/787742/guildford-grammar-preparatory-school-christou-design-group\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.ggs.wa.edu.au/About-Us/Our-School/Preparatory-School/Our-New-Preparatory-School-Buildings\">ggs</a></p>\n\n"}